nce, hours played, seniority, contribution to the guild, helping other members, phase of the moon, sexual favors, bribes, popularity, throwing the bones and or any number of other arcane/obscure/thankless means to attempt fair and impartial distribution of loot.<br>
<br>
All droppable loot is GUILD property and may not be traded sold or given to anyone else. An item no longer used it given back to the guild and redistributed to those in need. A person who leaves the guild for any reason is to return all droppable guild items as well.<br>
<br>
